<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[قوله]</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>: «على الَّتي تَلِيها <span class="c2">(٢)</span>»:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أي:</span> على رواية أهل المرتبة التي تليها.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قوله:</span> <span class="c2">«مِنْ قوَّةِ الضَّبْطِ»</span>:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">أي:</span>] و] <span class="c2">(٣)</span> زيادة العدالة.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[قوله]</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>: <span class="c2">«مَا يَنْفَرِدُ بِهِ»</span>:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>نائب فاعل <span class="c2">«يُعَدُّ»</span> وهو مفعوله الأول.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وقوله:</span> <span class="c2">«حَسَنًا»</span> هو مفعوله الثاني.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[قوله]</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>: <span class="c2">«عاصِم بن عُمَر»</span>:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">يعني:</span> ابن الخطاب.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[قوله]</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span>: <span class="c2">«عن جَدِّه»</span>:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هو عبد الله بن عَمرو بن العاص <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
